{"word":"ἐνεδρεύω","slug":"ἐνεδρεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐνεδρεύω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to lie in wait for</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>insidiari</el>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be caught in an ambush, to be ensnared</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to lay</i> or <i>set an ambush</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to lie in ambush</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}